---
title: Carb Smart 'BLT' Bacon and White Cheddar Farro with Spinach and Balsamic Roasted Tomatoes
description: This recipe has all the flavours of a traditional BLT, but whipped up into a delicious, hearty bowl of grains! Sweet burst tomatoes, spinach, crispy bacon and creamy farro – it's a combo that's sure to turn this sandwich classic into a dinner fit for royalty!

